Package com.gemalto.idp.mobile.otp.dsformatting.primitive

Interface HiddenTextPrimitive

All Superinterfaces:
Primitive, TextPrimitive
public interface HiddenTextPrimitive extends TextPrimitive
An interface representing a hidden text (E1) primitive.

This primitive has type Primitive.PrimitiveType.E1.

The allowed input format is TextPrimitive.TextFormat.BINARY.
